### 1. Design System Compliance

- Follow color, typography, spacing, and component standards.
- No inline or ad-hoc styles unless approved.

### 2. Component & Template Priority

- Use **shadcn/ui** components first.
- Leverage templates/layouts before writing custom code.
- Extend only when necessary.

### 3. Token Economy

- Keep responses minimal.
- No redundant explanations or duplicate code.

### 4. Git Workflow

- Never auto-push commits.
- GitHub pushes require explicit approval.
- Stage commits locally, wait for confirmation.
